Downsampling a PointCloud using a VoxelGrid filter
==================================================
see http://pointclouds.org/documentation/tutorials/voxel_grid.php

Make sure you have cmake installed.

Installing PCL
==============
Linux:
	see http://pointclouds.org/downloads/linux.html

Mac: download and install Homebrew (http://mxcl.github.com/homebrew/)
	In Terminal type: brew install pcl

For more detailed information please check: http://pointclouds.org/downloads/

Compiling the example
=====================
To compile and run the code, follow these steps:

mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..

Now the mafile should be there. Type this:

make
./voxel_grid 
